transcripts: this is the dyson v6 animal the most powerful vacuum that is both lightweight and cordless with seventy-five percent more brush bar power it is ideal for deep carpet cleaning but also underneath furniture stairs and up high. It is engineered to generate powerful cleaning performance throughout your home the small light motor has been developed specifically by Dyson to deliver powerful suction the dyson v6 animal removes more dirt and dust from the floors a mini motorized tool removes pet hair and ground in dirt from furniture cars and tight spaces it also comes with a mini soft dusting brush for delicate cleaning like computer keyboard the combination tool for surfaces like kitchen counters and a crevice tool for hard-to-reach places a direct drive clear head provide seventy-five percent more brush bar power to drive bristles deep into carpet.
